      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STATUE OF TIME (5) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.75 lengths at Angle Park in a handy 34.57 beating Echoes Of Dad. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. MOTOR CITY ROSSI (8) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at The Meadows over 600m behind Overland Boy (35.38) in a Grade 4/5. Was in the money prior to that. Better than last start and can bounce back. NIGHTTIME (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (30.12) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to his name from six starts. Expected to give a good account. MEPUNGA RULE (2) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts back but finished third last time (38.56) at Bendigo.",
